  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (f95fb9b 2023-08-23T00:16:31.166094919Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nforge test\n\n### Operating System\n\nLinux\n\n### Describe the bug\n\n```solidity\r\npragma solidity ^0.8.0;\r\n\r\nimport \"forge-std/Test.sol\";\r\n\r\ncontract PoC is Test {\r\n    function testNormal() public {\r\n        FOO foo = new FOO();\r\n        foo.foo();\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function testFooReturns() public {\r\n        FOO foo = new FOO();\r\n        FooReturn(address(foo)).foo();\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\ninterface FooReturn {\r\n    function foo() external returns(uint256);\r\n}\r\n\r\ncontract FOO {\r\n    function foo() external { }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis test should not revert, contracts that use USDT in ethereum for example will fail in local tests but not in mainnet, for example, this test would have to pass:\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\npragma solidity ^0.8.0;\r\n\r\nimport \"forge-std/Test.sol\";\r\n\r\nimport {IERC20} from \"openzeppelin-contracts/contracts/token/ERC20/IERC20.sol\";\r\n\r\ncontract PoC is Test {\r\n    address USDT = 0xdAC17F958D2ee523a2206206994597C13D831ec7;\r\n\r\n    function setUp() public {\r\n        vm.selectFork(vm.createFork(\"https://eth.llamarpc.com\"));\r\n\r\n        deal(USDT, address(this), 10 ether);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function testTransferWithIERC20() public {\r\n        IERC20(USDT).transfer(address(this), 10 ether);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function testTransferWithIUSDT() public {\r\n        IUSDT(USDT).transfer(address(this), 10 ether);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function testTransferWithContractUseIERC20() public {\r\n        FOO foo = new FOO(USDT);\r\n        deal(USDT, address(foo), 10 ether);\r\n        foo.transferIERC20();\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function testTransferWithContractUseIUSDT() public {\r\n        FOO foo = new FOO(USDT);\r\n        deal(USDT, address(foo), 10 ether);\r\n        foo.transferIUSDT();\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\ninterface IUSDT {\r\n    function transfer(address _to, uint _value) external;\r\n}\r\n\r\ncontract FOO {\r\n    address USDT;\r\n\r\n    constructor (address _USDT) {\r\n        USDT = _USDT;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function transferIERC20() external {\r\n        IERC20(USDT).transfer(msg.sender, 10 ether);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function transferIUSDT() external {\r\n        IUSDT(USDT).transfer(msg.sender, 10 ether);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```",
